{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987870/extras/titlecard.jpg?t=1726468798\" /><br><br>The Cerebral Escape Series is an omnibus that contains 3 different, first-person horror escape room games. It covers the genres of sci-fi, occult, and psychological horror where you must utilize your deduction &amp; observation skills to solve thrilling puzzles, as well as rely on your survival instincts to make your escape. Each game comes with their own unique scenario, where you must use your wits to make your escape from. But along the way, there are forces and entities that seek to hold you within\u2026<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987870/extras/Anachron_Title_Glitch.gif?t=1726468798\" /><br><br><strong>Anachron</strong> <br>Set in the far future of 2080, where humans have achieved space exploration and colonization. You play as an engineer waking up in a space station after an incident has occurred. You have to survive and find your way out by solving multiple puzzles while making your way to the escape pods. You have less than an hour before the whole station is consumed by a time rift. While trying to escape, you will encounter a dangerous presence that will try to stop you from leaving.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987870/extras/Pagan_Title_Dissolve.gif?t=1726468798\" /><br><br><strong>Pagan</strong><br>You are a girl who was kidnapped by a demon-worshipping cult, and confined within an abandoned temple for their ritual. But when they lose control of the summoning, you are now also trapped here alongside a malevolent demon\u2026<br><br>Make use of heretical magicks to progress through stages, while being pursued throughout the whole episode. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987870/extras/Splinters_Title_Shake.gif?t=1726468798\" /><br><br><strong>Splinters</strong><br>You wake up in an abandoned mental asylum, with no memories of who you are and plagued by mysterious visions. As you try to make your way out, you are followed by an entity\u2026<br><br>Go through notes and journal entries to escape this strange asylum, and perhaps even uncover your past.<br><br><br>Solve, Survive, Escape, or else\u2026","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987870/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1726468798","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987870/page.bg.jpg?t=1726468798","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987870/b50179f4363a292a08d0fd91089a26e82686c896/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1726468798","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987870/b50179f4363a292a08d0fd91089a26e82686c896/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1726468798","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Captions available","id":13}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987870/extras/titlecard.jpg?t=1726468798\" /><br><br>The Cerebral Escape Series is an omnibus that contains 3 different, first-person horror escape room games. It covers the genres of sci-fi, occult, and psychological horror where you must utilize your deduction &amp; observation skills to solve thrilling puzzles, as well as rely on your survival instincts to make your escape. Each game comes with their own unique scenario, where you must use your wits to make your escape from. But along the way, there are forces and entities that seek to hold you within\u2026<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2987870/extras/Anachron_Title_Glitch.gif?t=172646879